an></div><div>Cat tax! Dinah being breath takingly cute.  ?</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/BIE9gTm</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[shamelesspunner]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Buzz buzz</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NlrWu3N</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oRLgcT8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NlrWu3N</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Srajo101]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Last round of chemo!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/IU68nnP</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XC6HU9E.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>7 months off work, 6 months of chemo, and I’m finally on my last treatment! IV today then 2 weeks of chemo pills, so technically today is just the beginning of the end. 

I don’t get another scan for a couple months, so I’ll continue to keep my fingers crossed that this is the end of treatments. If anyone is willing to send positive vibes I’ll take ‘em! 

I’d like to say that this has changed my whole outlook, but truly I just can’t wait to get back to my normal life the best I can. Maybe that means I’m just incredibly lucky to have a life I was already happy with! My husband, family, friends, and kitties have all been amazing support and I can’t thank them enough. And thank you to the imgur community for keeping me entertained!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WVtrU2s.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Cat tax. My 2 babies Sookie and Neville                                                *edit* WOW! Front page and SO much support from my imgur family! You’re all so wonderful—thank you for celebrating with me. Cute story: due to Covid I can’t have anyone in treatments with me, so when I got into the car with my husband he had our families on FaceTime and a bell for me to ring! I have an amazing hubby!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/IU68nnP</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[casiehansolo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>How to spot a trans person (and other heartwarming stuff trawled up from the web)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/tuaAIzM</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/S1tCFpz.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nlAuxnL.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/daby3TA.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gHwjWGV.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QqquBKr.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Going to add my own story to this.

Me: Son, I'm trans.
Him (8 at the time): Really?

Me: Really.

Him: Really Really??

Me (on the edge of tears, barely holding it together, fearful of what his reaction might be): Yes, I'm a woman.

Him: ...

Me: I want you to know I'll always love you.

Him (deep in thought): ...

Me (tears rolling now): Do... do you have any questions?

Him: ... will I be let off my chores?
Me: No, you still need to empty the dishwasher.

Him: ... will I get extra candy?
Me: No, you having two mommies doesn't get you more candy.

Wife (nods firmly at the no-extra-candy rule)
Me: Do you have any more questions?
Him: ...can I tell you about the movie I just saw with grandma?

Me: Any questions about me being trans.
Him: So I use she and her for you now like for other girls?

Me: Yes.
Him: OK... I love you mommy. Anyway... grandmapickedmeupfromschool. WewenttothemoviesandgotpopcornandIhadawholethingofitand (pause for breath) thereisthiskidcalledBillyBatsonbuthebecomesSHAZAM! (pause for breath) andhefightsdemonsandtherewasawizardheisplayedbythe (pause for breath) guyfromchuckwhoplayschuckyouknowthespyand (pause for breath) hischestlightsupandhehaslightningandissuperstrongbutnotascoolatheFlash...</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/tuaAIzM</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ThatOtherGirlYouKnow]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>A moderately sized DK dump of stolen memes for these trying times 679.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/3T7DAej</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DWmiCQ7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WMItGol.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jJTAiiQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/97PFQ7P.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OkKXnhx.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oYba6rh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Eox9g3y.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/y7vABm7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hsj6AnN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BsFdSv1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%